\eqn{HR = \lambda / \lambda_0 < 1} (benefit). Two effect scales are considered:
\itemize{
\item Log-HR scale: \eqn{\log(\widehat{HR}_j) = \log(\hat{\lambda}_j / \lambda_0)}.
\item Linear-HR scale: \eqn{1 - \widehat{HR}_j = 1 - \hat{\lambda}_j / \lambda_0}.
